\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clara_Perez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clara_Perez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hawkshaw was unfortunate to see her effort in the 23rd minute bounce off one of the umpires.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The two sides reached half-time with no stoppages, no injuries, no cards and only one penalty corner registered.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spain made the brighter start after the restart, but goalscoring chances were at a premium as the match headed inexorably towards a penalty shootout.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.45135180995321e-13, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first two penalties were missed, with R\\u00f3is\\u00edn Upton failing to capitalise on Laia Vidosa opening miss.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Upton-by-Chester\", \"score\": 0.999999999829015, \"rank\": 1.7027111099328564e-10, \"text\": \"Upton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Upton-by-Chester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Upton-by-Chester\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lucia Jiminez put Spain in the driving before Hawkshaw spurned the chance to level matters.\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1583, \"end\": 1588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucia_di_Lammermoor\", \"score\": 0.9447506710778341, \"rank\": 0.05844739675705161, \"text\": \"Lucia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucia_di_Lammermo